While listening to the sample i caught a couple files that seemed relevant  
to me.  My Dad used to always call me "Stevie" so that might be him, could  
also be wishful thinking i suppose.  But the help file is very clear.   My 
Dad passed away last November, my guys keep telling me that he is helping  
over there.  I hope that it's true, but i'm sure nobody will hear these  
except maybe Frank.
 
-Steve H.
